class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>6<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></=
sup> given the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Variance#Definition=
" title=3D"Variance">definition</a> of variance and some <a href=3D"https:/=
/en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Variance#Properties" title=3D"Variance">properties</=
a> thereof. If <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><sp=
